1
00:01:36,570 --> 00:01:39,990
[NORTHWARD]

2
00:01:40,130 --> 00:01:42,009
[Episode 18]

3
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:01,750
There's some more here.

4
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:04,180
Here.

5
00:02:04,190 --> 00:02:05,850
I forgot I left it in my pocket.

6
00:02:10,259 --> 00:02:12,200
Boss, Haihong.

7
00:02:14,170 --> 00:02:15,870
You haven't eaten?

8
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:17,829
This is not much.

9
00:02:17,829 --> 00:02:18,910
You can use it first.

10
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:19,990
No, no.

11
00:02:19,990 --> 00:02:21,829
You need it yourself too.

12
00:02:21,829 --> 00:02:22,270
No.

13
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:23,350
No, take it.

14
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:24,190
Boss.

15
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,030
This matter

16
00:02:25,070 --> 00:02:27,420
happened because of this 10,000 yuan.

17
00:02:27,570 --> 00:02:29,890
As her mother, I made a mistake.

18
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:30,829
I didn't stop her

19
00:02:30,829 --> 00:02:32,329
from doing such a stupid thing,

20
00:02:32,329 --> 00:02:34,010
implicating Wanghe.

21
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:36,040
Wanghe did it for Fenghua.

22
00:02:36,070 --> 00:02:37,390
So take it.

23
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:39,420
Saving the child is more important.

24
00:02:39,510 --> 00:02:41,310
As you know,

25
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,430
our money is on the goods.

26
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:42,960
Yes.

27
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,840
Yes, we...

28
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:45,230
Gathering money?

29
00:02:46,890 --> 00:02:47,730
Here.

30
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:49,430
What are you doing?

31
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:50,829
You always meddle when something happens.

32
00:02:50,829 --> 00:02:52,150
Your money didn't fall from the sky.

33
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:53,910
No, it's an emergency.

34
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:55,390
Why are you talking so much?

35
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:56,590
Take it. I'm leaving.

36
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,860
Don't worry, Haihong.

37
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:02,550
Sorry.

38
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:04,180
We're really sorry.

39
00:03:04,180 --> 00:03:05,030
Don't worry.

40
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:05,750
Yanzi.

41
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:06,990
Let's stop at that.

42
00:03:06,990 --> 00:03:08,350
I won't stand on ceremony.

43
00:03:08,350 --> 00:03:09,190
I'll take

44
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:10,310
this money.

45
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:11,310
Also,

46
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:12,910
I remember

47
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:14,430
everyone's kindness.

48
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:15,430
We'll pay you back later.

49
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:16,430
No need.

50
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:19,110
We should pay for it.

51
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:20,870
Don't worry.

52
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:23,190
Eat first. Your health is more important.

53
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:24,190
I'm leaving.

54
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:27,430
Hurry up and eat.

55
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,310
Give it a count.

56
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:35,350
How much?

57
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:37,230
Siyi.

58
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:38,950
Grandma.

59
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:42,790
This is 2,000 yuan.

60
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,750
It's not much.

61
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:47,150
It's just to show our sincerity.

62
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:49,230
Take it to Ms. Liang.

63
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:50,829
Go.

64
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:52,750
I can't take this.

65
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,270
You owe too much. You don't want to live anymore?

66
00:03:54,270 --> 00:03:56,110
We are lending this to you. Not like you're not returning this.

67
00:03:56,110 --> 00:03:56,910
Right?

68
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:59,110
We're live in the same courtyard, I'm not afraid of you running away.

69
00:03:59,110 --> 00:04:00,390
Pay me back when you have money.

70
00:04:00,390 --> 00:04:02,050
Don't pay it back if you don't.

71
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:03,950
Thank Mr. Shao for me.

72
00:04:03,950 --> 00:04:05,550
Alright, go back.

73
00:04:07,070 --> 00:04:08,340
Siyi, you're here.

74
00:04:10,110 --> 00:04:11,020
Aunt Liang.

75
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,850
Grandma asked me to bring 2,000 yuan here.

76
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:16,230
Take it back.

77
00:04:17,180 --> 00:04:17,910
Take it back.

78
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,149
Grandma said it's our sincerity.

79
00:04:19,149 --> 00:04:20,640
We got it.

80
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:22,150
But bring the money back.

81
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,150
Take it.

82
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:23,990
Bring it back.

83
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:24,990
Tell Grandma

84
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:26,070
when I leave to drive the trucks,

85
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,950
allow Wanghe to have meals at your place.

86
00:04:27,950 --> 00:04:29,510
We'd appreciate that.

87
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:30,310
Yes.

88
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,150
Take it.

89
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:32,000
Bring it back.

90
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,200
Siyi, they've got us.

91
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,700
Go back and tell Grandma.

92
00:04:34,909 --> 00:04:36,310
We're here. Don't worry.

93
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,480
Go back in.

94
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:38,530
Be good.

95
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,830
Reassure your grandma.

96
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:42,360
They've got us, you don't have to do anything.

97
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,270
Granny...

98
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:44,420
Let's go back.

99
00:04:57,610 --> 00:04:58,970
That's all?

100
00:04:59,150 --> 00:05:01,880
It's about 100,000 yuan. There's a long way to go.

101
00:05:02,620 --> 00:05:03,740
Then let's

102
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,980
borrow more.

103
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:06,590
Anyway,

104
00:05:06,590 --> 00:05:07,740
I'll go drive with you.

105
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:08,620
Let's earn it slowly.

106
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:10,180
We can pay them back no matter what.

107
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:12,110
I've borrowed everything I could.

108
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,140
Who else can I look for?

109
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:26,400
It's not enough.

110
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,400
Can you give me another 20,000 yuan?

111
00:05:29,010 --> 00:05:31,170
I'm afraid you won't be able to pay back more than that.

112
00:05:31,170 --> 00:05:32,350
By driving the truck,

113
00:05:32,350 --> 00:05:33,880
I earn about 100,000

114
00:05:33,909 --> 00:05:35,390
I can make quite a lot of money.

115
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:38,150
I'll pay you back the principal and interest together when the time comes.

116
00:05:38,150 --> 00:05:39,210
Not a penny less!

117
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:43,440
It would be better if you had some collateral.

118
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,030
It's not that I don't trust you,

119
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:47,030
but I need to explain it to my family.

120
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,580
How about this?

121
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:50,930
At home,

122
00:05:51,020 --> 00:05:52,950
I have two pieces of gold jewelry.

123
00:05:53,130 --> 00:05:55,590
You can have them as collateral. How's that?

124
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:18,300
Fly!

125
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:19,510
Fly!

126
00:06:23,090 --> 00:06:23,980
Fly!

127
00:06:24,020 --> 00:06:24,940
Fly!

128
00:06:26,690 --> 00:06:28,930
The big plane is taking off!

129
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:32,950
Grandma,

130
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:35,070
I'll take you to fly over the Pacific Ocean.

131
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,900
All right, let's fly over the Pacific Ocean.

132
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:37,860
Play by yourself.

133
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,790
I'm tired. I'll take a rest.

134
00:06:39,820 --> 00:06:40,230
Okay.

135
00:06:40,230 --> 00:06:41,030
Go play.

136
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,830
I'm going to hit you!

137
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:52,950
Fly!

138
00:06:53,030 --> 00:06:53,720
Fly!

139
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:02,170
Fly!

140
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:03,670
Fly!

141
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,280
Take my

142
00:07:17,390 --> 00:07:18,310
punch!

143
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:22,830
Take my kick!

144
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:23,710
Oh no!

145
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:25,450
My hand has fallen off.

146
00:07:25,530 --> 00:07:28,290
Lao'er even went to ask Fenghua's aunt.

147
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:30,590
It's still not enough.

148
00:07:30,590 --> 00:07:33,170
We still have a lot to go despite adding it all together.

149
00:07:33,170 --> 00:07:34,480
They said

150
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:36,070
they didn't have much money left.

151
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:37,470
They said they're going to go borrow money.

152
00:07:37,470 --> 00:07:38,909
Who knows how much they can borrow?

153
00:07:38,909 --> 00:07:40,850
Don't borrow money from loan sharks.

154
00:07:40,850 --> 00:07:42,070
With the interest,

155
00:07:42,090 --> 00:07:44,180
you could go bankrupt.

156
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,520
Haihong must have gone to borrow money.

157
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,680
She can do anything

158
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:49,380
for Wanghe.

159
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:50,220
This morning,

160
00:07:50,230 --> 00:07:52,000
I saw her leave Flower Street.

161
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,190
She was in a hurry.

162
00:07:54,790 --> 00:07:55,909
What should we do?

163
00:07:56,110 --> 00:07:57,850
I saw those who borrowed from loan sharks

164
00:07:57,850 --> 00:07:58,560
would have their houses

165
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,320
taken away in the end.

166
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:01,140
Those people

167
00:08:01,170 --> 00:08:03,050
have no conscience, they smash and burn everything.

168
00:08:03,050 --> 00:08:04,560
They can do anything.

169
00:08:04,790 --> 00:08:05,550
Exactly.

170
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:07,420
One can never repay their high-interest loans.

171
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:08,890
Even when Wanghe's released from jail,

172
00:08:08,890 --> 00:08:10,030
he'd still have to shoulder this debt.

173
00:08:10,030 --> 00:08:11,110
Then this child

174
00:08:11,130 --> 00:08:12,740
will be doomed.

175
00:08:12,770 --> 00:08:15,280
Wanghe only took on this matter for Fenghua's sake.

176
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,880
Look at the mess we're in now.

177
00:08:17,990 --> 00:08:19,150
Watch this.

178
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:24,970
How dare you hit me!

179
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:27,280
Watch me turn into a fighter jet too!

180
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:36,309
Siwei, Grandma is resting.

181
00:08:36,390 --> 00:08:38,390
I'll take you to Fenghua's house for some treats.

182
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:39,110
Okay.

183
00:08:41,929 --> 00:08:44,010
To Fenghua's house!

184
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,390
Can you keep an eye on him for me?

185
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:09,150
I need to go out and take care of something.

186
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,930
Make sure you do your homework properly.

187
00:09:10,930 --> 00:09:12,260
What are you going to do?

188
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,150
Grandma is sick.

189
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,030
She can't cook.

190
00:09:14,070 --> 00:09:15,800
You're in charge of his dinner.

191
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,600
Sister.

192
00:09:31,980 --> 00:09:32,810
Siyi.

193
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:33,960
What's wrong?

194
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:41,060
Is your offer to lend me money still valid?

195
00:09:41,410 --> 00:09:42,940
Of course, it still stands.

196
00:09:43,530 --> 00:09:44,870
I have over 30,000 in my account.

197
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,000
How much do you need?

198
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:47,090
20,000.

199
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,740
I'll pay you back with bank interest later.

200
00:09:48,740 --> 00:09:49,270
No need.

201
00:09:49,710 --> 00:09:50,780
No, I've already–

202
00:09:50,810 --> 00:09:51,830
Let's do it your way, okay?

203
00:09:51,830 --> 00:09:52,810
All right, I'll go get my card.

204
00:09:52,810 --> 00:09:53,570
Wait for me.

205
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:57,520
Sis.

206
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:00,320
Sis?

207
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,240
Fenghua!

208
00:10:08,090 --> 00:10:09,770
I want to go see a movie.

209
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,120
"Iron Man."

210
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:12,220
It's interesting.

211
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:14,240
Everyone in my class has seen it.

212
00:10:14,250 --> 00:10:15,910
I'm the only one who hasn't.

213
00:10:16,740 --> 00:10:18,120
Have you finished your homework?

214
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,610
Yes, I have.

215
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,550
Let's go then.

216
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:23,600
I'm going to see "Iron Man"!

217
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:24,780
Hurry up!

218
00:10:24,810 --> 00:10:26,020
Slow down, slow down.

219
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:29,190
Sister, the Iron Man in there...

220
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:38,500
Ms. Liang.

221
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:40,850
Please take this money.

222
00:10:40,850 --> 00:10:42,120
Get Wanghe out quickly.

223
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,980
We can't let this affect his college entrance exam.

224
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:52,200
Where did you get so much money?

225
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:53,470
I didn't steal nor rob,

226
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:54,010
don't worry.

227
00:10:54,010 --> 00:10:55,870
It's within my personal means.

228
00:10:58,750 --> 00:10:59,730
No.

229
00:10:59,770 --> 00:11:02,700
You must explain clearly where this money came from.

230
00:11:04,190 --> 00:11:05,150
Ms. Liang,

231
00:11:05,170 --> 00:11:07,590
Wanghe's grades have improved rapidly recently.

232
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:08,690
If nothing goes wrong,

233
00:11:08,690 --> 00:11:10,390
he will definitely get into college.

234
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:10,990
At this time,

235
00:11:10,990 --> 00:11:13,450
freedom is the most important thing for him.

236
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,000
You don't need to see me out, Ms. Liang.

237
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
I'll be going now.

238
00:11:22,110 --> 00:11:23,240
Get some rest early.

239
00:11:32,890 --> 00:11:33,730
Grandma.

240
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:35,550
I'm back.

241
00:11:38,730 --> 00:11:40,590
Grandma, have you had dinner yet?

242
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,350
Grandma?

243
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,470
Grandma!

244
00:11:56,820 --> 00:11:57,940
Granny.

245
00:12:10,590 --> 00:12:14,040
[Police]

246
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:22,960
Thank you.

247
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:32,890
[If you admit your mistake, you can turn over a new leaf.]

248
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,350
Uncle.

249
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:35,530
I'm sorry.

250
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,720
[If you admit your mistake, you can turn over a new leaf.]

251
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:42,010
You need to use your brain when you do things in the future.

252
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:45,140
[If you admit your mistake, you can turn over a new leaf.]

253
00:12:44,990 --> 00:12:45,470
Go on.

254
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:47,310
They're waiting for you at home.

255
00:12:47,850 --> 00:12:49,770
Don't worry about Fenghua.

256
00:12:50,050 --> 00:12:51,030
We've watched him

257
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,930
delete all the photos in his records,

258
00:12:52,930 --> 00:12:55,180
and punished him according to the law.

259
00:13:00,530 --> 00:13:05,230
[Police]

260
00:13:14,070 --> 00:13:14,800
Wanghe.

261
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:20,550
Have a good talk with your father when you get home.

262
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:21,750
Don't make him angry.

263
00:13:23,570 --> 00:13:24,570
Thank you, Uncle.

264
00:13:49,570 --> 00:13:50,700
Where's your uncle?

265
00:13:51,810 --> 00:13:54,270
He said he had something to do and left early.

266
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:56,430
Dad.

267
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,520
Mom.

268
00:13:59,450 --> 00:14:00,290
I'm sorry.

269
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:02,950
I've caused trouble for the family again.

270
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,670
Sit down and eat.

271
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:10,900
Sit down, sit down.

272
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:21,970
Come on.

273
00:14:25,420 --> 00:14:26,280
Thank you, Dad.

274
00:14:27,530 --> 00:14:29,280
I'm not used to the food inside.

275
00:14:38,620 --> 00:14:40,350
You should eat too, Mom and Dad.

276
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:42,970
In the future,

277
00:14:45,470 --> 00:14:46,820
before you do anything,

278
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:48,630
you need to use your head.

279
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,680
You can't be so impulsive anymore.

280
00:14:52,990 --> 00:14:54,790
For your college entrance exam,

281
00:14:54,970 --> 00:14:56,500
we had to pay that Pang Dahai

282
00:14:56,890 --> 00:14:58,620
100,000 yuan in compensation.

283
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:01,920
100,000?

284
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,150
On what grounds?

285
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:07,110
Do you know what that bastard did?

286
00:15:07,230 --> 00:15:08,230
If we didn't pay the 100,000,

287
00:15:08,230 --> 00:15:09,570
they would refuse mediation,

288
00:15:09,570 --> 00:15:12,360
and you would...

289
00:15:13,190 --> 00:15:14,710
You would be kept in there.

