295
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:23,040
I'd rather die

296
00:15:23,070 --> 00:15:25,530
than bow down to these thugs and scoundrels!

297
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:27,220
Can you be mature?

298
00:15:29,070 --> 00:15:31,150
Isn't that what you taught me, Dad?

299
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:33,710
You said a person should have a sense of responsibility.

300
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:35,870
Yes, I was impulsive this time,

301
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:37,640
but my intentions were good.

302
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:39,660
