306
00:16:37,420 --> 00:16:38,280
I'm not hungry.

307
00:16:51,710 --> 00:16:53,190
At the end of the day,

308
00:16:53,510 --> 00:16:54,830
it's really my fault.

309
00:16:57,400 --> 00:16:58,330
You

310
