312
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:09,000
and was even proud of it.

313
00:17:09,530 --> 00:17:11,190
Standing up for justice, huh?

314
00:17:16,079 --> 00:17:17,089
Well,

315
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:18,829
you did that

316
