319
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:26,530
without considering the consequences.

320
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:30,900
This is a problem that needs to be solved.

321
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:39,470
Dad,

322
00:17:41,020 --> 00:17:42,480
I was impulsive this time,

323
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,350
but I don't think I was wrong.

324
00:17:47,190 --> 00:17:50,530
That bastard bullied Fenghua

325
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:52,080
and uploaded those photos.

326
00:17:52,410 --> 00:17:53,660
If I were a coward,

327
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:56,030
who knows what might happen in the future?

328
00:17:58,020 --> 00:18:00,750
So I absolutely refuse to bow down to such people.

329
00:18:01,360 --> 00:18:03,430
I was protecting my family and friends.

330
00:18:03,430 --> 00:18:04,310
Was I wrong?

331
00:18:16,130 --> 00:18:17,990
To compensate them that 100,000,

332
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,700
the neighbors

333
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:21,270
chipped in.

334
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:23,830
We also

335
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:25,680
borrowed

336
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,160
some money

337
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:30,600
but it still wasn't enough.

338
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:35,510
After Siyi learned about this,

339
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:37,800
she ran out

340
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:40,310
to borrow money from her classmate.

341
00:18:42,610 --> 00:18:44,010
By the time she came back,

342
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,450
Granny Ma had already passed away.

343
00:18:49,970 --> 00:18:51,570
It was cerebral hemorrhage.

344
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:54,180
Because there was no one around,

345
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:56,790
she didn't get timely rescue.

346
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:59,220
I feel...

347
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:11,780
Grow up quickly.

348
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:15,090
Your mother and I are old.

349
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:18,240
We can't keep up with your antics anymore.

350
00:20:00,290 --> 00:20:01,300
Eat up.

351
00:20:02,950 --> 00:20:04,060
I'm not hungry.

352
00:20:04,090 --> 00:20:05,950
You haven't eaten for a whole day.

353
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:07,440
Hurry up.

354
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,550
I said I'm not hungry.

355
00:21:01,110 --> 00:21:02,330
Grandma.

356
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:06,710
I'm back.

357
00:21:10,390 --> 00:21:11,440
The doctor said

358
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,740
Grandma passed away in her sleep.

359
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,700
She left peacefully.

360
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:19,960
Last night,

361
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:22,990
I dreamed about Grandma.

362
00:21:24,870 --> 00:21:26,300
She told me

363
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:28,700
she's been very tired lately

364
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,520
and wanted to take a break.

365
00:21:31,860 --> 00:21:33,460
She asked me not to blame her.

366
00:21:35,530 --> 00:21:37,350
I knew it was a dream,

367
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,350
so I told her in the dream

368
00:21:41,290 --> 00:21:42,330
not to leave.

369
00:21:45,870 --> 00:21:47,490
But she left anyway.

370
00:21:55,230 --> 00:21:56,960
I just went out for a moment,

371
00:21:58,100 --> 00:22:00,430
