372
00:22:35,850 --> 00:22:36,490
Dad...

373
00:22:37,730 --> 00:22:38,630
Mom...

374
00:22:39,700 --> 00:22:40,670
I'm sorry.

375
00:22:42,460 --> 00:22:43,690
I was wrong.

376
00:22:52,460 --> 00:22:54,810
I'm sorry, I was wrong.

377
00:22:58,270 --> 00:22:59,210
This matter,

378
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,950
at the very bottom of it,

379
00:23:04,450 --> 00:23:06,150
is your responsibility.

380
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:12,630
From now on,

381
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,310
be better to Siyi.

382
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:19,210
Do your best in this lifetime

383
00:23:20,180 --> 00:23:22,260
to spare her from suffering.

384
00:23:24,930 --> 00:23:27,520
This is what you owe Granny Ma.

385
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,050
Don't cry anymore.

386
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:51,950
Go to bed early.

387
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:55,570
You have school early tomorrow morning.

388
00:23:56,830 --> 00:23:58,820
I feel terrible inside.

389
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:00,800
We all do.

390
00:24:04,910 --> 00:24:06,630
All these years, Granny Ma

391
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:10,580
has been so good to us.

392
00:24:11,090 --> 00:24:12,580
She left so suddenly.

393
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:18,050
