394
00:24:21,370 --> 00:24:22,470
That day...

395
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:25,960
Siyi asked me to watch her place...

396
00:24:27,860 --> 00:24:29,650
I didn't take it seriously...

397
00:24:30,820 --> 00:24:33,050
I even took Siwei to watch a movie.

398
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:37,230
If we had been at home,

399
00:24:38,150 --> 00:24:40,350
Granny Ma wouldn't have passed away...

400
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,990
Don't think like that.

401
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:49,060
Cerebral hemorrhage is very dangerous to begin with.

402
00:24:49,930 --> 00:24:51,840
Even if we had taken her to the hospital,

403
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:53,970
we might not have been able to save her.

404
00:24:58,560 --> 00:25:01,430
At least there would have been a glimmer of hope.

405
00:25:03,820 --> 00:25:05,600
It's all my fault.

406
00:25:06,210 --> 00:25:09,680
I shouldn't have gone out.

407
00:25:16,550 --> 00:25:18,150
Don't cry.

408
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:57,460
Sister.

409
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,120
I'm hungry.

410
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:02,640
There are instant noodles. Make it yourself.

411
00:26:02,890 --> 00:26:04,510
I don't want instant noodles.

412
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:06,040
They give me a stomachache.

413
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:31,380
Go buy something to eat yourself.

414
00:26:32,150 --> 00:26:33,390
Are you eating?

415
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,130
I'm not hungry.

416
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:39,990
But you haven't eaten for two days.

417
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:49,010
Go and come back quickly.

418
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:51,040
Sis,

419
00:26:51,190 --> 00:26:53,590
please go and eat something with me.

420
00:26:56,580 --> 00:26:57,670
Fine.

421
00:26:57,990 --> 00:26:59,510
I'll go eat by myself then.

422
00:27:03,730 --> 00:27:04,660
Hello, Grandpa.

423
00:27:33,740 --> 00:27:36,420
Go to the shop for a bowl of eel noodles later.

424
00:27:36,610 --> 00:27:38,540
You can't keep starving yourself.

425
00:27:39,350 --> 00:27:40,400
No need.

426
00:27:41,060 --> 00:27:42,120
I'm not hungry yet.

427
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:44,480
Thank you, Grandpa Zhou.

428
00:27:45,910 --> 00:27:47,270
If you get hungry,

429
00:27:50,250 --> 00:27:53,080
your grandma will come to our dreams and scold us.

430
00:27:56,260 --> 00:27:57,470
She wouldn't do that.

431
00:27:57,930 --> 00:27:59,190
Who says she wouldn't?

432
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,810
Don't you remember?

433
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:03,030
That year,

434
00:28:03,350 --> 00:28:05,370
when you and Wanghe went down to the river

435
00:28:05,370 --> 00:28:06,430
to learn how to swim

436
00:28:06,740 --> 00:28:08,140
and choked on some water,

437
00:28:09,140 --> 00:28:11,140
someone mimicked it to your grandma

438
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:14,120
and it made her so mad.

439
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:18,450
She went door to door scolding everyone, young and old.

440
00:28:19,590 --> 00:28:22,670
None of us had a peaceful meal that day.

441
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:27,030
I remember Wanghe and Haikuo both got hit.

442
00:28:27,730 --> 00:28:30,800
Xiaopang ran away from home after just two hits.

443
00:28:32,190 --> 00:28:33,790
That incident scared me too.

444
00:28:34,620 --> 00:28:36,670
You were your grandma's soft spot.

445
00:28:41,770 --> 00:28:42,740
Except for her,

446
00:28:43,490 --> 00:28:44,750
no one could touch you.

447
00:28:47,780 --> 00:28:48,980
Last month,

448
00:28:49,860 --> 00:28:50,880
on a night,

449
00:28:53,110 --> 00:28:55,350
your grandma suddenly came to my house.

450
00:28:57,650 --> 00:28:58,780
Mr. Zhou,

451
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:00,860
I

452
00:29:01,210 --> 00:29:04,270
have had someone write a power of attorney. Have a look.

453
00:29:07,330 --> 00:29:10,590
In case I...

454
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:14,220
I'll have to trouble you...

455
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:16,270
to help me sell that house.

456
00:29:16,620 --> 00:29:18,830
You can keep the money,

457
00:29:18,910 --> 00:29:20,950
and you can give it to Siyi monthly.

458
00:29:21,060 --> 00:29:24,770
We must ensure Siyi finishes university, no matter what.

459
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:26,440
If...

460
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:29,340
If this money isn't enough,

461
00:29:32,540 --> 00:29:33,540
then

462
00:29:34,630 --> 00:29:36,830
I'll have to trouble everyone.

463
00:29:40,310 --> 00:29:42,140
I'm sorry to everyone.

464
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:46,980
I...

465
00:29:48,450 --> 00:29:52,240
I can only repay this in my next life.

466
00:30:03,050 --> 00:30:04,250
I'm counting on you.

467
00:30:12,380 --> 00:30:15,990
We'll talk about whether we have to sell the house later.

468
00:30:18,290 --> 00:30:20,740
This time, I represent

469
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:23,370
the neighbors from this courtyard

470
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:25,370
to tell you that you

471
00:30:26,950 --> 00:30:29,900
don't need to worry about money.

472
00:30:30,190 --> 00:30:32,050
Even if you study for a doctorate,

473
00:30:32,340 --> 00:30:33,630
we'll support you.

474
00:30:38,710 --> 00:30:39,700
I know

475
00:30:40,320 --> 00:30:42,030
if this happened to another family,

476
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:44,030
and if another child was left alone,

477
00:30:44,040 --> 00:30:45,820
as long as Granny Ma was around,

478
00:30:46,690 --> 00:30:49,030
even if she had scrimp and save,

479
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:51,580
she wouldn't stand by and watch.

480
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:57,920
We all know

481
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:01,300
you're independent and strong-willed,

482
00:31:02,120 --> 00:31:03,330
but

483
00:31:03,350 --> 00:31:05,340
you should accept everyone's kindness

484
00:31:05,340 --> 00:31:06,940
on behalf of

485
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:07,760
your grandma.

486
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:13,340
From this moment on,

487
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:15,240
you,

488
00:31:15,740 --> 00:31:16,910
Ma Siyi,

489
00:31:17,820 --> 00:31:19,320
are the child

490
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,870
of all of us.

491
00:31:29,070 --> 00:31:30,590
Grandpa Zhou...

492
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:44,260
Look, look.

493
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,260
What are you doing?

494
00:31:45,260 --> 00:31:45,750
Shoo.

495
00:31:45,910 --> 00:31:47,280
Don't cause trouble here.

496
00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:48,140
Go over there.

497
00:31:57,870 --> 00:31:58,800
You messed it up.

498
00:32:02,520 --> 00:32:03,530
You're back?

499
00:32:05,150 --> 00:32:06,020
How did it go?

500
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:06,840
How was it?

501
00:32:08,910 --> 00:32:09,770
Mr. Zhou.

502
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:14,100
I've talked to Siyi.

503
00:32:15,810 --> 00:32:18,190
