504
00:32:18,520 --> 00:32:19,600
So,

505
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:21,780
later,

506
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:23,860
everyone should pay more attention.

507
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:25,250
Communicate with her regularly.

508
00:32:25,250 --> 00:32:26,670
It's the last semester.

509
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:28,190
It's crucial.

510
00:32:29,170 --> 00:32:31,260
We must not let it affect her grades.

511
00:32:31,590 --> 00:32:33,020
Siyi is a good child.

512
00:32:33,050 --> 00:32:34,670
She has always been sensible.

513
00:32:34,670 --> 00:32:36,330
If it were just her alone,

514
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:37,730
there's no need to worry.

515
00:32:37,730 --> 00:32:38,770
But she has

516
00:32:38,990 --> 00:32:40,270
a younger brother.

517
00:32:41,290 --> 00:32:43,810
Someone needs to pick him up from school.

518
00:32:43,910 --> 00:32:45,470
She has to cook when they get home.

519
00:32:45,470 --> 00:32:47,030
And help with his homework.

520
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:51,620
I feel for this child just thinking about it.

521
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:54,620
Siyi is still just a teenager herself.

522
00:32:54,650 --> 00:32:56,520
It's not easy for her to take care of herself,

523
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:57,460
