524
00:32:57,460 --> 00:32:58,570
and preparing for the college entrance exam.

525
00:32:58,570 --> 00:33:00,030
It's definitely too much.

526
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:02,850
Actually, if you ask me,

527
00:33:04,750 --> 00:33:07,250
we should all try to persuade Siyi's mother

528
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:09,430
to take Ge Siwei back with her first.

529
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:11,540
At least for this semester.

530
00:33:12,070 --> 00:33:14,330
We can't let this affect Siyi's studies.

531
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:15,960
What if she refuses?

532
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:17,950
That mother of hers

533
00:33:18,470 --> 00:33:19,910
is not a good person.

534
00:33:20,990 --> 00:33:22,450
How can you talk like that?

535
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:23,590
No matter what,

536
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:25,000
they're still her own children.

537
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:26,120
When Granny was around,

538
00:33:26,120 --> 00:33:26,820
she left him here.

539
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:27,790
Now that she's gone,

540
00:33:27,790 --> 00:33:30,130
she still won't take care of her own son?

541
00:33:30,150 --> 00:33:31,580
You never know.

542
00:33:31,910 --> 00:33:33,110
Given the old lady's situation before,

543
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:34,650
