544
00:33:34,650 --> 00:33:36,440
That's right, she was extorting the old lady.

545
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:37,610
As if the old lady owed her something.

546
00:33:37,610 --> 00:33:38,510
Exactly.

547
00:33:38,530 --> 00:33:39,180
Well then,

548
00:33:40,420 --> 00:33:42,130
let's see her attitude first.

549
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:44,020
If she's friendly,

550
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:46,760
we'll be polite to her.

551
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:47,950
Right?

552
00:33:48,990 --> 00:33:50,850
Let's try not to fall out with her.

553
00:33:51,110 --> 00:33:51,740
Yes, yes.

554
00:33:52,170 --> 00:33:54,560
If she's unreasonable,

555
00:33:56,290 --> 00:33:57,950
we'll pressure her together.

556
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:01,030
We won't let her bully the children.

557
00:34:01,510 --> 00:34:02,320
-Yes.
-Yes.

558
00:34:02,790 --> 00:34:03,380
Exactly.

559
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:07,570
Siyi can't keep pushing herself like this.

560
00:34:07,570 --> 00:34:10,570
If she continues like this, her health will collapse.

561
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:13,540
