565
00:34:20,830 --> 00:34:21,510
If this continues,

566
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:23,840
her health will definitely deteriorate.

567
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:30,420
Did you see Granny

568
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:32,690
before she passed?

569
00:34:34,120 --> 00:34:34,940
No.

570
00:34:39,030 --> 00:34:41,560
By the time we found out, she was already gone.

571
00:34:51,620 --> 00:34:52,820
We won't be able to eat

572
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:56,560
those fried radish cakes anymore.

573
00:35:04,550 --> 00:35:06,520
Who knew this would happen?

